potato /pəˈteɪtəʊ/

(potatoes) 

1. N-VAR Potatoes are round vegetables with brown or red skins and white insides. They grow under the ground. 土豆 

2. PHRASE You can refer to a difficult subject that people disagree on as a hot potato . 烫手山芋 

例： ...a political hot potato such as abortion. …像堕胎这样的政治性烫手山芋。

